# Teste da API de Gerenciamento de Usuários
# Use este arquivo com extensões como REST Client no VS Code

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Registrar usuário
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com",
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123"
}

### Obter perfil (substitua o token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Atualizar perfil
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva Santos"
}

### Alterar senha
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/password
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "MinhaSenh@123",
  "newPassword": "NovaSenha@456"
}

### Obter estatísticas do usuário
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/stats
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Solicitar recuperação de senha
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/password/reset-request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@exemplo.com"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/logout
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Logout de todos os dispositivos
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### Excluir conta
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/account
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "MinhaSenh@123"
}